                    <run bold='true'>📶 </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontsize='10'>Fiber optic users show highest </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontsize='10'>churn risk</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true'>💳 </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontsize='10'>Electronic check customers churn </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontsize='10'>the most</run>
